" ***Question 1: \"How likely is it that Bond will escape from Le Chiffre?\"***\n4. Neutral or Uncertain\n\nAlthough Bond was able to put up a brief struggle, the passage ends with him feeling \"puny and impotent.\" Without further context, it is uncertain if or how Bond might escape from Le Chiffre and his gunmen.\n\n***Question 2: \"How suspenseful do you find this passage to be?\"***\n6. Very suspenseful\n\nThis passage is very suspenseful as it describes the sudden and unexpected capture of Bond by Le Chiffre and his men, as well as the brief struggle that ensues. The reader is left in suspense as to what will happen next and how Bond will manage to escape this dangerous situation."